 src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e238cf2e60a3db4f56f8a893e7468ecaf969e5f9","tid":841454,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:03:59.000Z","msg":"電子煙有冇害，係可以科學論證，可以化驗啲煙，可以幫個人驗身<br />\n<br />\n港獨係政治選擇，係喜好黎，冇分對錯，你唔會話一對情侶分手係對定錯，唔岩key就分開"},{"pid":"813273d5a99feff6b519f5989fd2fb9e817c74f4","tid":841454,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817c717f03ba3f201daad38e2709b9461be5704c","tid":841454,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:11:17.000Z","msg":"中資未出到出名嘅電子煙啫，睇死中資一出、政府就會一百八十度轉"},{"pid":"6ae2ea79c21634e4881ddf5f41ec76f60077ac2c","tid":841454,"uid":57407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:12:47.000Z","msg":"咁都拉到落去港獨 真港獨之父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d763a363536e9743cc85865659cb97ceaf410d4","tid":841454,"uid":46358,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"禁唔禁電子煙又幾時變咗一言堂？<br />\n<br />\n依家正正就係香港班醫學界教育界恃住自己有話語權，為咗要禁電子煙就直接老屈<br />\n<br />\n明明人哋英國佬已經有幾百萬人靠電子煙唔食煙佢就話冇證據幫到戒煙<br />\n<br />\n明明人哋話電子煙都係有害但一定冇煙咁有害佢就淨係係咁話有害<br />\n<br />\n就係多得689依班咁反智嘅人香港先有人會講港獨"},{"pid":"ac0c1e18e0ab2ba1540fef280a2db8b8e232d804","tid":841454,"uid":31652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T16:54:23.000Z","msg":"689係咪 Mr. A"},{"pid":"c409027340b4526c9820eac10841482a84644551","tid":841454,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T16:55:56.000Z","msg":"放心啦,紀念碑實落你名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684ef795ec862efc3ea5ecb319d478bcf2a32c9a","tid":841454,"uid":46538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T17:00:19.000Z","msg":"政府成日話電子煙仲毒過真煙既原因<br />\n係因為真煙有稅收<br />\n電子煙冇稅收<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講真萬寶路果隻電子煙對比起真煙黎講陣味真係少左好多<br />\n而人地玩花式果d電子煙更加唔會好似政府所講係咁有害<br />\n<br />\n真煙同電子煙都食過 <br />\n真煙食完體能真係會差左<br />\n電子煙（冇尼古丁、焦油果d ）食完只係會覺得個鼻成日會好多油"}]}